QUESTION/1/OVESETUP_APACHE_CONFIG_SSL=str:automatic
QUESTION/1/OVESETUP_CONFIG_ADMIN_SETUP=str:**********
QUESTION/1/OVESETUP_CONFIG_APPLICATION_MODE=str:both
